Package edu.uiowa.cs.warp

Class Channels

java.lang.Object
edu.uiowa.cs.warp.Channels
public class Channels extends Object
This class represents a set of channels available for communication at different time slots. It provides methods to manage and manipulate these channels.
Version:
1.4
Author:
sgoddard
